    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc214856n520as56241491423048">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Letters from thirty artists to Sue Scott, Curator, Oklahoma Art Center, 1987-1988, concerning their work in the Westheimer Collection. This information was collected preparatory to an exhibition of the Westheimer Collection. Excerpts from the letters are used in exhibition catalog, a copy of which is included.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc214856n520as66520255899979">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Correspondents include Karel Appel, Will Barnet, Gene Bavinger, Robert Beauchamp, Aaron Bohrod, Isabel Case Borgatta, Carolyn Brady, Roy Carruthers,Christin Couture, Rackstraw Downes, Don Eddy, John Fincher, Janet Fish, Rosalie Gwathmey, Paul Jenkins, Alex Katz, Josef Levi, David Levine, Jack Levine, Richard McLean, Ulisse Pagliari, Peter Paone, Philip Pearlstein, Joseph Raffael, Deborah Remington, Wade Reynolds, Larry Rivers, David Soyer,George Tooker, and Robert Vickrey.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <bioghist id="aspace_hzc214856n545as87679662448643">
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>Art museum curator; Oklahoma.</p>
    </bioghist>
